{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"0wwj1byxg3uhkh6el05q2o9","title":"Data+AI Summit 2022 키노트 주요 어나운스먼트 요약","desc":"","updated":1669900626710,"created":1667314080000,"custom":{},"fname":"dev.data+ai.databricks.data+ai-summit-2022-keynote-summary","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"ad2d8da966fd949b13528e7d9afce462","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"dev.data+ai.databricks.data+ai-summit-2022-keynote-summary","id":"0wwj1byxg3uhkh6el05q2o9","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"dev.data+ai.databricks.delta_lake","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":7,"offset":48},"end":{"line":4,"column":44,"offset":85},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"dev.data+ai.databricks.delta_lake"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"dev.data+ai.databricks.data+ai-summit-2022-keynote-summary","id":"0wwj1byxg3uhkh6el05q2o9","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"dev.data+ai.spark.structured_streaming","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":17,"offset":347},"end":{"line":17,"column":59,"offset":389},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"dev.data+ai.spark.structured_streaming"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"dev.data+ai.databricks.data+ai-summit-2022-keynote-summary","id":"0wwj1byxg3uhkh6el05q2o9","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"dev.data+ai.databricks.delta_live_tables","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":4,"offset":421},"end":{"line":20,"column":48,"offset":465},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"dev.data+ai.databricks.delta_live_tables"}}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"skeuhenz2vf0ycgfmyy8pl1","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"dataai-summit-2022-키노트-주요-어나운스먼트-요약\">Data+AI Summit 2022 키노트 주요 어나운스먼트 요약<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#dataai-summit-2022-키노트-주요-어나운스먼트-요약\"></a></h1>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Delta Lake 2.0</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Storage layer 역할</li>\n<li><a href=\"/pks-publish/notes/f5ta5qp6kvcp8x23oxfjwi2\">Delta Lake</a> 오픈소스화</li>\n<li>github에서 2.0.0 확인 가능</li>\n<li>데이터브릭스 플랫폼에서만 제공하던 기능을 오픈</li>\n<li>성능과 관리 퍈의성을 획기적으로 개선</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Spark Spark</p>\n<ul>\n<li>이론적인 실제적인 공로를 인정받음</li>\n<li>Spark Connect</li>\n<li>Spark를 모든 곳에서 쓸 수 있게.</li>\n<li>OOM?</li>\n<li>씬 클라이언트에서도 Spark 사용 가능</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Project Lightspeed</p>\n<ul>\n<li>차세대 Spark <a href=\"/pks-publish/notes/cmfutyhgtl88lr1sike6zta\">Structured Streaming</a> </li>\n<li>더 빠르고 심플한 스트림 프로세싱</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/pks-publish/notes/hvd8818q6qo5xxfok5lhye7\">Delta Live Tables</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>ETL Framework 서비스</li>\n<li>Enzyme 옵티마이저 -> 증분 ETL 작업</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Databricks SQL Serverless</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Unity Catalog</p>\n<ul>\n<li>모든 데이터 및 AI asset을 통합 관리하기 위한 기능</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"rfaecb1r4pxpahsrighqpfi","title":"Dev","desc":"","updated":1666489926104,"created":1666489926104,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"dev","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"5f3d9b993bc1c60c0e10119b00a45c49","links":[],"anchors":{},"children":["vmcgt1bw13lwsobet50r3vl","pj0dbesw2qm5j1tub9f34pg","e40hlh2wukm75vo4t8r9c7p","7xwnx64er01irhu8wg1q5zm","4buyekecqhzdg87aqxmh1rz","n1xmefdyaaztqb8wmsmqtjj","d8p9jq81rc0pfbbuzz7prah","yq2839iijurmzkrwkqwo9ps","xuw6kyksesfaatsmt3gctyi","d3ma1d2r59fhejrl6bn9g0e","tgd9pt1fu1j4ejm4g09vlx4","5jlkrg4hx6dpy5tr55grkh6","owsm2ti22dslhpk9oduhhku","52x2zgp7jpygai1h0jpv0t8"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":""},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templa